Sentencas: Effects of SO2 in ambient air on the performance and durability of solid oxide fuel cell(SOFC) cathode were evaluated by galvanostatic measurement.
Titulo: Effect of SO2 on Performance of Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Cathodes

Sentencas: Comparison between two cathode materials was made to consider the cathode degradation mechanisms.
Titulo: Effect of SO2 on Performance of Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Cathodes

Sentencas: The degradation performance is associated with a slow decomposition of the La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3(LSCF) due to the segregation of strontium oxide.
Titulo: Effect of SO2 on Performance of Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Cathodes

Sentencas: Negligible deterioration for (La0.7Sr0.3)MnO3 (LSM) cathode was caused by SO2 poisoning under a current density of 200 mA/cm(2).
Titulo: Effect of SO2 on Performance of Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Cathodes

Sentencas: Metal sulphate formation may explain a slight deterioration under increasing high the concentration of SO2.
Titulo: Effect of SO2 on Performance of Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Cathodes

Sentencas: It was verified that the poisoning mechanism for the two cathode materials resulted from the gradual decomposition of the cathode materials.
Titulo: Effect of SO2 on Performance of Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Cathodes
